1
00:00:16,016 --> 00:00:17,809
Don't be afraid, Miss Velma.

2
00:00:17,892 --> 00:00:21,312
It's hard to fight a person you love so much.

3
00:00:21,730 --> 00:00:23,982
I will do everything to fix this.

4
00:00:24,482 --> 00:00:27,277
So I can push myself towards the right path.

5
00:00:28,069 --> 00:00:29,070
What's the plan?

6
00:00:29,279 --> 00:00:31,990
This won't be easy for all of us.

7
00:00:32,449 --> 00:00:35,075
You used me to get everything you wanted.

8
00:00:35,076 --> 00:00:36,870
And that includes Velma Beauty.

9
00:00:36,911 --> 00:00:38,496
Let’s just leave it at that.

10
00:00:39,539 --> 00:00:40,957
What a scheming, manipulative...

11
00:00:41,082 --> 00:00:42,792
Be careful, Shari.

12
00:00:42,834 --> 00:00:46,254
[NOREEN] We need everyone to believe
that we are still fighting.

13
00:00:47,589 --> 00:00:48,465
Second,

14
00:00:49,799 --> 00:00:51,885
we will be enemies.

15
00:00:54,679 --> 00:00:59,601
Soon, you are going to be
receiving invitations to the Velma Ball.

16
00:00:59,684 --> 00:01:03,021
That already includes two people close to my heart.

17
00:01:03,563 --> 00:01:07,609
Shari de Jesus and Noreen Alfonso.

18
00:01:07,984 --> 00:01:09,569
Forgive me.

19
00:01:12,405 --> 00:01:15,324
Please be with me during my last days.

20
00:01:15,325 --> 00:01:16,242
Oh my gosh.

21
00:01:16,243 --> 00:01:18,369
Mom. Can you please
be less dramatic?

22
00:01:18,495 --> 00:01:20,079
[SOBS]

23
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:22,082
Because you’re going to get better.

24
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:28,671
You're going to get better and we will start over.

25
00:01:30,048 --> 00:01:32,425
I just need to do something important.

26
00:01:34,677 --> 00:01:37,180
This is part of my efforts
to change my life, Mom.

27
00:01:37,472 --> 00:01:39,057
[SOBS]

28
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:44,728
I have no idea why you’re filled
with anger and loneliness.

29
00:01:44,729 --> 00:01:48,316
[NOREEN SOBS]

30
00:01:48,858 --> 00:01:50,860
But hopefully,

31
00:01:52,654 --> 00:01:56,282
you won’t forget the real you.

32
00:01:56,825 --> 00:02:00,453
[NOREEN SOBS AND SNIFFLES]

33
00:02:02,664 --> 00:02:03,998
Stop crying now.

34
00:02:07,585 --> 00:02:08,878
[HUMMING]

35
00:02:09,546 --> 00:02:17,846
[GANDA GANDAHAN BY DIA MATE PLAYING]

36
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:56,301
Your ball is all set, Miss V.

37
00:02:57,343 --> 00:03:00,388
And Eddie wants you arrested there.

38
00:03:05,101 --> 00:03:10,815
Kriselda is still working on getting
the CCTV footage of my sister’s murder.

39
00:03:12,817 --> 00:03:15,778
That’s why we will need a huge distraction.

40
00:03:16,154 --> 00:03:17,989
We must act fast, Noreen.

41
00:03:18,615 --> 00:03:20,033
Tell us the plan.

42
00:04:11,167 --> 00:04:14,671
What is that girl doing here, crashing our party?

43
00:04:14,837 --> 00:04:16,004
No, she’s not.

44
00:04:16,005 --> 00:04:18,007
I invited her here.

45
00:04:18,925 --> 00:04:20,051
What?

46
00:04:20,843 --> 00:04:22,636
After what she did to us?

47
00:04:22,637 --> 00:04:25,515
She tried taking us both down, Velma.

48
00:04:26,266 --> 00:04:27,934
Yes, she’s here.

49
00:04:28,101 --> 00:04:31,311
She’s here to witness the greatest show on earth.

50
00:04:31,312 --> 00:04:34,315
And we will all go to hell together!

51
00:04:35,066 --> 00:04:36,733
What are you talking about?

52
00:04:36,734 --> 00:04:38,569
What’s happening to you?

53
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:41,531
I’ve already woken up to the truth, Eddie.

54
00:05:37,337 --> 00:05:38,379
[KRISELDA] Miss V?

55
00:05:39,464 --> 00:05:41,174
The standby room is ready for you.

56
00:05:41,382 --> 00:05:43,926
Please stay there while
waiting for the grand reveal.

57
00:05:47,305 --> 00:05:48,473
Velma.

58
00:06:38,648 --> 00:06:41,025
You will die during your ball, Miss Velma.

59
00:06:43,111 --> 00:06:44,445
Oh my God.

60
00:06:47,323 --> 00:06:48,783
A fake death.

61
00:06:49,742 --> 00:06:51,953
Why do we have to fake my death?

62
00:06:52,203 --> 00:06:53,996
What will I even look like?

63
00:06:55,706 --> 00:06:59,419
You need to disappear, Miss Velma.

64
00:07:00,128 --> 00:07:03,047
It’s the only way to stop them from arresting you.

65
00:07:41,711 --> 00:07:44,380
Miss V’s throne is ready.

66
00:07:44,714 --> 00:07:46,799
There’s just one thing missing.

67
00:07:47,341 --> 00:07:50,219
The bloody queen herself.

68
00:07:51,554 --> 00:07:55,558
Let’s give them a show they will never forget.

69
00:08:28,132 --> 00:08:32,386
This is what Noreen meant when she
said that we need to play Eddie’s game.

70
00:08:33,596 --> 00:08:40,269
So we’re faking it to reverse it?

71
00:08:41,562 --> 00:08:43,814
So they will arrest Eddie

72
00:08:44,106 --> 00:08:46,359
because we don’t
have a video yet?

73
00:08:47,902 --> 00:08:50,196
Eddie is not going to be arrested.

74
00:08:55,284 --> 00:08:56,702
Then who will be arrested?

75
00:09:26,315 --> 00:09:28,400
Alright, Velma, you've gotta
give me something here.

76
00:09:28,401 --> 00:09:29,609
I... [SCOFFS]

77
00:09:29,610 --> 00:09:31,237
What is going on? What's this...

78
00:09:31,862 --> 00:09:33,446
“Waking up to the truth?” What truth?

79
00:09:33,447 --> 00:09:36,450
The truth that I loved a heartless monster!

80
00:09:36,659 --> 00:09:37,660
Okay.

81
00:09:39,453 --> 00:09:42,415
Have you been talking to Noreen and Shari?

82
00:09:42,957 --> 00:09:44,834
And about what this time?

83
00:09:45,293 --> 00:09:46,752
About that thing again?

84
00:09:47,086 --> 00:09:48,169
That I raped Helena?

85
00:09:48,170 --> 00:09:48,754
Until now?

86
00:09:48,755 --> 00:09:50,506
I thought we were past this, Velma!

87
00:09:51,007 --> 00:09:54,634
I will not shut up
until you answer me, Eddie!

88
00:09:54,635 --> 00:09:56,344
I already answered your questions!

89
00:09:56,345 --> 00:09:57,305
I gave you everything!

90
00:09:57,305 --> 00:09:58,264
What more do you want from me?

91
00:09:58,264 --> 00:09:59,223
The truth-

92
00:09:59,224 --> 00:10:01,391
that you’re a rapist
and a sexual predator!

93
00:10:01,392 --> 00:10:02,310
That’s enough!

94
00:10:02,476 --> 00:10:03,519
You’re pissing me off!

95
00:10:03,769 --> 00:10:04,687
Enough!

96
00:10:07,231 --> 00:10:09,524
Just tell me the truth!

97
00:10:09,525 --> 00:10:12,320
That you had something to do
with what happened to Helena!

98
00:10:12,945 --> 00:10:14,362
That you drugged her!

99
00:10:14,363 --> 00:10:15,488
You raped her!

100
00:10:15,489 --> 00:10:16,782
You killed her!

101
00:10:16,949 --> 00:10:17,783
You murdered her!

102
00:10:17,784 --> 00:10:18,950
You’re a murderer!

103
00:10:18,951 --> 00:10:20,161
That’s enough!

104
00:10:22,038 --> 00:10:24,457
You’re still accusing me of doing those things?

105
00:10:25,082 --> 00:10:26,751
I thought we were done with this!

106
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:28,628
Until when?

107
00:10:29,295 --> 00:10:30,463
Until when, Velma?

108
00:10:30,796 --> 00:10:31,672
I’m done with this.

109
00:10:31,673 --> 00:10:32,923
It ends today!

110
00:10:33,591 --> 00:10:34,883
You’re always accusing me.

111
00:10:34,884 --> 00:10:36,218
When will it end?

112
00:10:36,469 --> 00:10:37,345
Go ahead.

113
00:10:37,345 --> 00:10:38,095
Do it.

114
00:10:38,096 --> 00:10:39,137
Keep pinning it on me.

115
00:10:39,138 --> 00:10:40,180
See what happens.

116
00:10:40,181 --> 00:10:41,057
I’m telling you.

117
00:10:41,058 --> 00:10:42,224
I will really kill you.

118
00:10:42,558 --> 00:10:43,225
Alright!

119
00:10:43,226 --> 00:10:44,810
Kill me then!

120
00:10:45,895 --> 00:10:48,689
When you lied to me, you already used me!

121
00:10:48,981 --> 00:10:50,732
You used me, you manipulated me!

122
00:10:50,733 --> 00:10:51,567
You lied to me!

123
00:10:51,568 --> 00:10:53,861
It’s as if you already killed me, Eddie!

124
00:10:54,362 --> 00:10:57,782
And that’s my fault, huh, Velma?

125
00:10:58,658 --> 00:11:01,202
You made it so easy, Velma.

126
00:11:02,578 --> 00:11:03,954
Because you’re desperate.

127
00:11:04,747 --> 00:11:06,831
Everything I said, you believed it.

128
00:11:06,832 --> 00:11:08,334
Even when you knew it wasn't true.

129
00:11:09,418 --> 00:11:11,003
So you’re admitting it?

130
00:11:11,545 --> 00:11:13,171
You’re admitting that you’re a rapist!

131
00:11:13,172 --> 00:11:14,965
That you killed Helena!

132
00:11:19,345 --> 00:11:20,553
Admit it!

133
00:11:20,554 --> 00:11:22,765
So what if I did?

134
00:11:25,601 --> 00:11:27,436
That makes me a monster?

135
00:11:33,901 --> 00:11:35,611
So what if I am?

136
00:11:40,991 --> 00:11:42,118
- Hmm?
- [VELMA GASPS]

137
00:11:42,243 --> 00:11:43,244
What are you gonna do?

138
00:11:43,828 --> 00:11:45,454
You'll stab me in the chest?

139
00:11:45,746 --> 00:11:46,247
Huh?

140
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:47,873
You will tell everyone?

141
00:11:49,291 --> 00:11:55,297
I'm telling you, before you could even
start talking, I would’ve already killed you.

142
00:11:57,174 --> 00:11:59,634
Do it!

143
00:11:59,635 --> 00:12:02,096
I’d rather die than live in hell with you!

144
00:12:08,144 --> 00:12:09,978
[EDDIE SCREAMS]

145
00:12:09,979 --> 00:12:12,022
- [EDDIE SNARLS]
- [VELMA GASPS]

146
00:12:12,982 --> 00:12:16,610
[VELMA PANTS]

147
00:12:24,243 --> 00:12:26,203
[VELMA SOBS]

148
00:12:29,331 --> 00:12:31,000
[DOOR SLAMS]

149
00:12:33,669 --> 00:12:38,215
[VELMA SOBS]

150
00:12:40,926 --> 00:12:44,346
[VELMA CRYING]

151
00:13:07,119 --> 00:13:09,121
His fingerprints are there.

152
00:13:09,705 --> 00:13:12,875
I can’t wait for that monster to go to hell.

153
00:13:27,973 --> 00:13:32,603
I know what you’re going through
is painful and difficult, Miss V.

154
00:13:34,647 --> 00:13:36,065
We’re nearly there.

155
00:13:37,024 --> 00:13:41,278
We will be able to finally tell the whole
world the evil things your husband did.

156
00:13:42,488 --> 00:13:44,782
But we need to do this first.

157
00:13:47,243 --> 00:13:49,703
You’ll finally be free of him, Miss V.

158
00:13:50,162 --> 00:13:52,373
Did you capture everything?

159
00:13:52,915 --> 00:13:54,208
Everything.

160
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:57,211
I was able to capture everything.

161
00:13:58,295 --> 00:13:59,755
Thank you so much.

162
00:14:00,381 --> 00:14:02,258
Well, I guess...

163
00:14:02,466 --> 00:14:05,094
it’s time we set off the bomb.

164
00:14:07,429 --> 00:14:10,599
Shari and Kriselda are already
preparing the next step.

165
00:14:25,781 --> 00:14:27,825
[MIGOY] Eddie won't be the one to be arrested.

166
00:14:29,451 --> 00:14:30,578
Then who will be?

167
00:14:33,372 --> 00:14:34,331
[NOREEN EXHALES SHARPLY]

168
00:14:39,003 --> 00:14:40,462
It’s you, Shari.

169
00:14:48,262 --> 00:14:49,555
M-Me?

170
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,640
[STUTTERS] Oh, come on, Noreen.

171
00:14:52,641 --> 00:14:54,852
This face doesn’t belong in jail!

172
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:57,897
And Noreen...

173
00:14:58,230 --> 00:15:00,357
I don’t want to be imprisoned!

174
00:15:00,733 --> 00:15:01,525
I know.

175
00:15:02,818 --> 00:15:03,861
Let me explain.

176
00:15:04,945 --> 00:15:10,159
[SIGHS] It will only be a matter of time
before Eddie realizes our plans.

177
00:15:12,286 --> 00:15:14,955
I’m sorry, but we have to do this.

178
00:15:15,998 --> 00:15:18,584
We need to get ahead of him.

179
00:15:18,876 --> 00:15:22,838
Because if he catches us, he will kill us all.

180
00:15:23,589 --> 00:15:26,467
[NOREEN SIGHS] This is the best
plan we could think of. I'm sorry.

181
00:15:26,842 --> 00:15:29,762
This is also the only way,
so Eddie won’t be able to escape.

182
00:15:30,721 --> 00:15:35,100
We are sure that if Miss Velma
gets arrested, Eddie will flee.

183
00:15:37,978 --> 00:15:39,980
Eddie needs to stay here.

184
00:15:40,105 --> 00:15:42,815
So we get to monitor his movements
without him realizing

185
00:15:42,816 --> 00:15:44,610
that we’re all pulling the strings.

186
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:50,699
The only way he stays
is if his wife dies.

187
00:15:55,079 --> 00:15:57,873
You will be freed, don’t worry.

188
00:15:59,458 --> 00:16:03,212
Eventually, all evidence will point
to him without his knowledge,

189
00:16:03,671 --> 00:16:05,798
until he is arrested.

190
00:16:09,009 --> 00:16:10,970
[SHARI SIGHS DEEPLY]

191
00:16:12,596 --> 00:16:15,099
Well, you better make sure this works, Noreen.

192
00:16:16,141 --> 00:16:18,352
Or else I’ll put you in jail, too.

193
00:16:22,064 --> 00:16:24,692
Shari, fate is on our side.

194
00:16:25,401 --> 00:16:27,236
So don’t worry.

195
00:16:32,032 --> 00:16:33,951
Are you okay with this, Miss Velma?

196
00:16:35,411 --> 00:16:37,496
[EXHALES SHARPLY]

197
00:16:38,372 --> 00:16:41,125
As long as I die a glamorous death, then,

198
00:16:41,792 --> 00:16:43,293
I guess, count me in.

199
00:16:43,794 --> 00:16:45,379
Won’t Eddie get suspicious of this?

200
00:16:47,464 --> 00:16:49,717
He’s already neck deep in my trap.

201
00:16:50,718 --> 00:16:54,179
He truly believes we’re on the same side.

202
00:16:56,432 --> 00:16:58,225
[SIGHS DEEPLY]

203
00:16:58,517 --> 00:16:59,351
Noreen.

204
00:17:01,812 --> 00:17:03,272
When I go to jail,

205
00:17:04,815 --> 00:17:07,735
can you make sure that
I will be freed quickly?

206
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:16,452
I got you, Shari.

207
00:17:18,203 --> 00:17:20,955
Noreen, I really can’t stay there for long.

208
00:17:20,956 --> 00:17:22,332
[SHARI SIGHS]

209
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:27,087
I have other things in my life
that needs my full attention.

210
00:17:28,630 --> 00:17:30,382
I understand, Shari.

211
00:17:32,176 --> 00:17:34,178
Don’t worry, it will be quick.

212
00:17:35,095 --> 00:17:37,097
You will be freed.

213
00:17:52,154 --> 00:17:54,073
Is everything ready?

214
00:17:58,827 --> 00:18:01,163
I already prepared everything we need.

215
00:18:01,663 --> 00:18:03,123
We’re just waiting for one thing.

216
00:18:15,594 --> 00:18:17,846
[VELMA] Thank God you’re finally here.

217
00:18:18,430 --> 00:18:20,432
I’ll keep watch outside.

218
00:18:23,018 --> 00:18:24,603
Don’t worry, Shari.

219
00:18:25,687 --> 00:18:27,523
You’ll get out of this.

220
00:18:27,856 --> 00:18:29,233
I guarantee it.

221
00:18:29,525 --> 00:18:33,112
We just need to make it look like you killed me,

222
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:34,947
so Eddie can’t get away.

223
00:18:38,033 --> 00:18:39,408
I trust you both.

224
00:18:39,409 --> 00:18:40,577
Are you ready?

225
00:18:41,745 --> 00:18:43,079
Let the show begin.

226
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:44,748
Where is your wife?

227
00:18:45,332 --> 00:18:48,710
Isn’t this the grand launch of Velma
that she's been bragging about?

228
00:18:49,711 --> 00:18:51,380
Isn’t she going to face me?

229
00:18:51,630 --> 00:18:53,006
Uh, no, she’s here.

230
00:18:54,216 --> 00:18:55,926
She’s not trying to hide from you.

231
00:18:59,054 --> 00:19:00,347
What happened?

232
00:19:04,268 --> 00:19:05,894
This will slow down your heartbeat.

233
00:19:06,854 --> 00:19:09,273
So they will believe that you really died.

234
00:19:10,524 --> 00:19:11,692
Huh?!

235
00:19:14,153 --> 00:19:16,321
My God, Miss V!

236
00:19:16,613 --> 00:19:17,614
You!

237
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:18,949
Huh!?

238
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:21,410
- You killed Miss Velma!
- No!

239
00:19:21,660 --> 00:19:22,869
What happened!?

240
00:19:22,870 --> 00:19:23,912
Velma, no!

241
00:19:24,246 --> 00:19:25,747
I'm not a murderer!

242
00:19:25,914 --> 00:19:27,373
I could never kill Miss Velma!

243
00:19:27,374 --> 00:19:29,418
[EDDIE SCREAMING] What did you do!?

244
00:19:29,877 --> 00:19:31,545
[EDDIE CRYING] Velma!

245
00:19:33,172 --> 00:19:35,090
I got it before they were able to find it.

246
00:19:36,008 --> 00:19:38,343
[EDDIE] My fingerprints are on that.

247
00:19:38,927 --> 00:19:40,303
You know what to do with that.

248
00:19:40,304 --> 00:19:42,556
No one must know that I held that.

249
00:19:43,140 --> 00:19:45,934
Station 13... De Jesus!

250
00:19:46,351 --> 00:19:48,478
You have a call. Emergency.

251
00:19:50,772 --> 00:19:52,691
[SHARI WAILING] Just leave, get out!

252
00:19:52,816 --> 00:19:55,568
Get out, because you betrayed me!

253
00:19:55,569 --> 00:19:56,945
You lied to me!

254
00:19:56,987 --> 00:20:00,406
You abandoned me here, Noreen, so leave!

255
00:20:00,407 --> 00:20:03,160
I don't need you, I don't trust you anymore!

256
00:20:03,202 --> 00:20:04,703
Get out of here!
